FBIS4-63764 "drsov101_d_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 Regional Affairs Defense Ministry Denies Fire at Pacific Fleet Storage Defense Ministry Denies Fire at Pacific Fleet Storage LD2405180094 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1704 GMT 24 May 94 LD2405180094 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] [Text] Moscow May 24 TASS -- The Russian Ministry of Defence refuted today reports claiming fire at the Pacific Fleet's storage of combustibles and lubricants on May 23. According to the ministry's Press and Information Department, the fire broke out at a civilian oil storage, which has nothing to do with the fleet.
